The French paediatric cohort of Castleman disease: a retrospective report of 23 
patients.

Borocco C(1), Ballot-Schmit C(2), Ackermann O(3), Aladjidi N(4), Delaleu J(5), 
Giacobbi-Milet V(6), Jannier S(7), Jeziorski E(8), Maurier F(9), Perel Y(4), 
